To all the people who r frequently saying that this should be disliked...
it's a request to them that they should think before commenting.. the original singers #sabribrothers of this qawali are its pioneers and they were and they are the best qawals of not only this subcontinent but of this entire world. So, no one can do their own stuff better than them, where Atif is a rock star and he has done a true justice with this qawali and he has refreshed the soul of this soulful and ever beautiful qawali... so please stop saying that for god sake.
ajj is Coke studio ki waja se hamari young generation ko pta chala hey k sabri brothers b koi aye thay hamare Pakistan mein and they were the best.
These things are necessary for the revival of these beautiful tracks , qawali's etc,
